GYA surveys: summary statistics

As of Tue Jul 19 09:29:07 2016, 1978 surveys from 66 countries have been completed.

The majority of surveys were completed by researchers based in Canada (n = 1247), followed by Israel (n = 178) then by USA (n = 101) and the UK (n = 133).
